mg\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765350/extras/e217ba65e280d7fa0f4770be4eb31691.avif?t=1762226860\" width=600 height=718 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765350/extras/1229f45b7f45d0c081b891eed706361f.webp?t=1762226860\" width=600 height=28 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765350/extras/48f1fa31ba1ff4cbbe5c3347ac95006e.avif?t=1762226860\" width=600 height=729 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765350/extras/0a0a9d638c3f92bdf88669823b74c17a.webp?t=1762226860\" width=600 height=18 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765350/extras/df556e1f369fb16e6e956d900ad03108.webp?t=1762226860\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765350/extras/b1dba804a74788421103d38997751c50.avif?t=1762226860\" width=600 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　　<strong>KID Fans Club</strong>是一个以Galgame为主题的社区 / 汉化组 / 同人社团，成立于2002年7月11日。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　　在20多年的时间里，我们几乎见证了中文Galgame的整个发展历程，也一直在努力将业界优秀的Galgame作品进行中文本地化。只是，我们的梦想不止于此，我们更加希望有朝一日，本土文化的作品能够茁壮发展、开枝散叶。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　　临渊羡鱼，不如退而结网。「候鸟」是我们的第一部原创Galgame，也承载着我们的梦想与期望。希望她能够给您带来一些与众不同的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　　交流群：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　　主群：<strong>993606376</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　　备用群：<strong>512423117</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >　　微博 & B站：<strong>KIDFansClub</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\">